Python Configuration
Step 1. Add python interpreter using docker-compose yaml file
Step 2. Specify start script
Step 3. Set environment variable "PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1"
Step 4. Set path mapping

Python Tests Configuration
Step 1. Specify target module name
Step 2. Set additional arguments "--override-ini=addopts="" -vv -s --verbose"
Step 3. Set environment variable "FLASK_DEBUG=1"
Step 4. Set working directory
Step 5. Set path mapping
Step 6. Set interpreter
